{"article_id":"M4oedI6uXS0zB9dG","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Ukrainian passenger jet","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that crashed shortly after takeoff from Tehran on Wednesday","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"was accidentally shot down by an Iranian anti-aircraft missile ,","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"western security officials believe .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"Justin Trudeau calls for investigation into Iran plane crash","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"as Canada mourns","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Read more","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"Intelligence sources told","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"their assessments suggest","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"two surface-to-air missiles had targeted the Ukraine International Airlines Flight 752","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that went down in Iran on Wednesday morning ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"killing all 176 people onboard .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"Iran was inviting experts from Boeing , the jetliner ' s manufacturer , to join the investigation into the crash ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"the Iranian official news agency IRNA said on Friday ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"while the US National Transportation Safety Board said","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"it had received \" formal notification \" of the crash from Iran","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"and had designated a representative to the crash inquiry .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Iran ' s aviation authority had said earlier","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"it would not hand over flight recorders to either Boeing or US aviation authorities","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"but would give Ukrainian investigators access to the inquiry .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Play Video","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"' I want answers ' :","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Justin Trudeau says","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"missile downed plane in Iran - video","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"The Canadian prime minister , Justin Trudeau , said","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"his government \" will not rest \"","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"until it got justice .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"\" We have intelligence ,","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"including from our allies and own intelligence","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"that the plane was shot down by Iranian surface-to-air missiles , \"","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"Trudeau said .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"\" Canadians want answers .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"That means transparency , accountability and justice . \"","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Western agencies are understood to have picked up signals of the missile launches","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"followed by the traces of an explosion .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"A British source said :","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"\" The assessment is that it looks like it is a tragic accident . \"","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"In a statement on Thursday night , Boris Johnson said :","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"\" There is now a body of information","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"that the flight was shot down by an Iranian surface-to-air missile .","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"This may well have been unintentional .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"We are working closely with Canada and our international partners","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"and there now needs to be a full , transparent investigation . \"","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"Play Video 0:31","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Iran video appears to show missile striking Ukrainian plane","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"- video","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Of the 176 people onboard , 78 were Iranian ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"63 were Canadian","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"and 11 were Ukrainian","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"( including nine crew members ) ,","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"along with 10 Swedes , seven Afghans , four Britons and three German nationals .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"There was some confusion over the nationality of those killed","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"with many holding dual citizenship .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"The passenger aircraft crashed in farmland on the outskirts of Tehran","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"a few hours after Iran had launched more than a dozen missiles at US forces","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"stationed in Iraq ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"during a period","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"when Revolution Guards commanders say","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"they were expecting an imminent American response","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"and were on high alert .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"The revelation","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"that the plane might have been shot down","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"will prompt a reassessment of the consequences of Donald Trump ' s decision","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"to assassinate the Iranian general Qassem Suleimani last week , an escalation of hostilities","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"that brought the region to the brink of all-out conflict .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Play Video 3:40","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Why did Trump order the killing of Iran 's Qassem Suleimani ?","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"- video explainer","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Iranian officials on Thursday rejected the western intelligence assessments .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"\" Scientifically , it is impossible that a missile hit the Ukrainian plane ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"and such rumours are illogical , \"","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"Ali Abedzadeh , the head of Iran ' s of Civil Aviation Organisation told a state-run media outlet .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Separately , US media outlets quoted officials","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"their satellites had identified the signature of an Iranian anti-aircraft battery","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"being activated","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"shortly before the aircraft went down","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"a few minutes after taking off at 6.13am on Wednesday morning .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"The US officials said","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"they had identified infrared signals from two suspected missiles ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"followed shortly afterwards by an infrared blip from the burning aircraft .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"Play Video","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"Iran Press TV video shows fiery aftermath of Ukrainian plane crash in Iran","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"Trump told reporters on Thursday","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"he had \" suspicions \"","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"the plane might have been mistakenly shot down .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"\" Someone could have made a mistake on the other side , \"","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"\" Some people say","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"it was mechanical ,","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"I personally don ' t think","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"that ' s even a question .","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"I have a feeling","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"that ... something very terrible happened. \"","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"The Pentagon declined to comment .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"Public suspicions","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"that the Boeing 737-800 may have accidentally been shot down","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"had grown throughout Thursday","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"based on images","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"circulating on social media","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"showing what appeared to be missile debris","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"that was purportedly photographed near the crash site .","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"Facebook Twitter Pinterest","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"Images","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"circulating online","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"of what an Iranian activist said","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"was a missile head","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"photographed near the crash site .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"The London-based firm IHS Markit cited the images in a memo","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"arguing","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"the aircraft was \" likely to have been shot down mistakenly by an IRGC-operated SA-15 missile \" .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"It said","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"the debris appeared to be that of a Russian-made Tor-M1 missile","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"known to be possessed by Iran ' s Revolutionary Guards .","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"It could not confirm the authenticity of the images","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"but said","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"it assessed them to be credible .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"Iranian investigators had said earlier on Thursday","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"their preliminary conclusion was that the plane had suffered a catastrophic technical problem ,","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"caught on fire","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"and crashed","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"as it tried to return to Tehran ' s Imam Khomeini International airport .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"They confirmed","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"they had recovered the aircraft ' s two black boxes , recording instruments","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"designed to survive a high-impact crash ,","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"but said","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"the devices appeared to have suffered damage","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"and could have been missing some memory .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"Hassan Rezaeifar , the head of the committee","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"that oversees aviation accidents in Iran ,","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"told the state-run Islamic Republic news agency","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"that a special meeting had been called","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"to consider the possibility","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"the plane was shot down ,","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"but dismissed it .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"\" As the pilot of the Ukrainian plane was trying to get back to the airport ,","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"the scenario of a missile attack ... is off the table , \"","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"\" This has been discussed in a special session","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"and went off the table . \"","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"investigators had rejected the veracity of the images","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"purporting to show missile debris at the site .","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"\" No parts of a missile were found at the scene of the crash , \"","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"Iranian authorities had said","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"the crash was likely to be the result of technical issues","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"almost immediately after announcing","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"the plane had gone down shortly after 7am local time on Wednesday morning","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"( 3.30am GMT ) .","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"The Ukrainian government had initially endorsed that assessment","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"but changed its position hours later ,","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"no longer ruling out the possibility","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"the aircraft had met with foul play","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"and urging a full and transparent investigation .","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"By Thursday morning , Ukraine ' s top national security official was openly discussing in a Facebook post the possibility","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"the aircraft may have been shot down .","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"\" Our commission is currently agreeing with the Iranian authorities to travel to the place of the crash ,","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"and plans to search for debris of a","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"[ Russian-made ]","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"surface-to-air Tor missile ,","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"according to information","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"which was published on the internet , \"","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"Oleksiy Danilov said .","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"A Ukrainian investigative team was at the crash site on Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":165,"text":"And the Iranian government spokesman , Ali Rabiei said","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"that any country","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"which lost citizens on the flight","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"would be welcome to send representatives .","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"The head of the official Iranian Investigative Committee , Hassan Rezaeifar , said","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"that the US had also been invited , as the home nation of the plane ' s manufacturer , Boeing ,","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"according to the country ' s semi-official Fars news agency .","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"Play Video","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"Video purportedly shows moment","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"Ukrainian passenger plane plummets near Tehran","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"Some members of the Ukrainian investigative team had been involved in the inquiry into the 2014 shooting down of Malaysia Airlines flight MH17 over eastern Ukraine by Russian-armed rebels ,","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"Danilov added .","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"\" We will use all our best practices","depth":11},{"id":178,"text":"from investigating the attack on MH17","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"to find out the truth in the case of the Ukrainian plane in Tehran , \"","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"Iran ' s aviation authority said on Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":182,"text":"it would not hand over flight recorders either to the aircraft ' s American manufacturer or to US aviation authorities ,","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"but that it would give Ukrainian investigators access to the investigation .","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"But Ali Abedzadeh appeared to backtrack on Thursday ,","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":186,"text":"claims in the Iranian media","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"that the black boxes would not be sent overseas","depth":11},{"id":18